QuestData.Title: Return to Atuik
QuestData.Description: Return to Elder Atuik at Kamagua. He and the rest of my people must be warned of this impending doom that approaches from the sea.$B$B<Orfus shivers.>$B$BUse the Ancient Lift to reach him. Please hurry!
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the bad news to Elder Atuik at Kamagua.
QuestData.RewardText: The Kalu'ak thank you for all that you have done, $n. We must now prepare for battle and warn our brothers and sisters across the sea of what is to come.$B$BI hope it is not too late...
